snippet.title: Amber Valletta | The Conversation With Amanda de Cadenet | L/Studio created by Lexus
snippet.description:
From picketing power plants to becoming a power player, supermodel Amber Valletta chats about being a fashion renegade with her eco-friendly clothing line, a killer in the boardroom and a trailblazer in the bedroom.
